description: Nanao Akane is the manager of the baseball club who has a secret relationship with http://anidb.net/ch128820 [Katase Shouya]. She formerly took part in swimming, though had to quit due to her large breasts; after quitting, she was impressed by Shouya working hard in the club and decided to join. However, due to relationships being banned between club members, Akane was blackmailed into having a sexual relationship with the coach once he found out about it.
name: Nanao Akane
